Description:
WOW! THIS ONE WON'T LAST LONG
"Undoubtably one of the best buys in Officer."
Located only minutes from Cardinia train station, shopping centre and some of the finest schools in the area, there is no arguing the location is as good as it gets. On top of this, 23 Hampshire Street is a well-proportioned four bedroom home with plenty of room in the backyard.
Featuring:
- Four massive bedrooms, master with walk-in robe and en-suite;
- Open plan living/dining room at the rear of the house;
- The fourth bedroom on the north side can be converted back to another living area if needed;
- Well appointed modern kitchen with walk-in pantry;
- Ducted heating and split system cooling;
- Single car garage with remote control access and internal door to the inside of the home;
- Large backyard.
Ready to be sold.

MUST HAVE MILLER
"A well proportioned house on one of the bigger blocks available in Officer."
On a block spanning well over 500sqm is a near-new home that is a versatile 22 squares. Dotted in the popular Arcadia Estate and only moments from schools, shops and public transport systems the property is also very close to the proposed retail precinct.
The property is an ideal first home or for the astute investor who is aware that to make a decent return you need to ensure you've purchased a good-sized block.
As an added bonus you have large side access perfect for anyone with boats, caravans, trailers etc.
The property itself features:
- 3 bedrooms, master with walk-in robe and en-suite;
- Theatre room;
- Open plan living/dining area;
- Large, open kitchen with upgraded appliances;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car garage;
- Block size of 513sqm approx.
